## Git Workflow

### Pre-commit Hooks

Configured in [package.json](mdc:package.json):

```json
{
  "lint-staged": {
    "src/**/*.{js,jsx,ts,tsx}": "eslint --fix",
    "src/**/*.{js,jsx,ts,tsx,css,scss,md}": "prettier --write --ignore-unknown"
  }
}
```

### Branch Naming

- Prefer ticket-based branches: `{number}/{transformed_name}` (e.g. `42/fix_drawer_close_button`) — see [new-branch-rule.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/new-branch-rule.mdc)
- Legacy: `feature/description`, `fix/description`, `hotfix/description`

